{"tid":533555,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"1823又請人","createTime":"2018-01-19T01:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T03:14:42.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c08fbf823ed7fe29225ed10d77c6fd348ecbceaa","tid":533555,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:44:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://csboa1.csb.gov.hk/csboa/jve/JVE_003.action?jobid=39723&amp;extractDto.mark=&amp;languageType=1&amp;extractDto.showCheckList=Y&amp;extractDto.onlineGF340=Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcsboa1.csb.gov.hk%2Fcsboa%2Fjve%2FJVE_003.action%3Fjobid%3D39723%26extractDto.mark%3D%26languageType%3D1%26extractDto.showCheckList%3DY%26extractDto.onlineGF340%3DY&d=6mpiucgFL%2B7RJizNolVLEuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=881bdd60\" target=\"_blank\">https://csboa1.csb.gov.hk/csboa/jve/JVE_003.action?jobid=39723&amp;extractDto.mark=&amp;languageType=1&amp;extractDto.showCheckList=Y&amp;extractDto.onlineGF340=Y</a><br />\n<br />\n聽講合約期3星期，避418<br />\n有無人可以confirm?"},{"pid":"582cbf338ddcc65275e2930dac2446fc081156d1","tid":533555,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:44:55.000Z","msg":"咩係418<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8296f1a3794a42ad675f17de494389f51eec0a70","tid":533555,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:45:18.000Z","msg":"你仲想打政府工？<br />\n唔驚？"},{"pid":"0f0fbbb70661e8dfa16a5736ed0e3016a5583b28","tid":533555,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582cbf338ddcc65275e2930dac2446fc081156d1","tid":533555,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:44:55.000Z","msg":"咩係418<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"勞工法例知多D<br />\n<br />\n4.18<br />\n俗稱4.18的勞工法例，即指工友如果連續受僱4星期，每星期的工時又不少於18小時，工友的合約便是「連續性合約」，會受到勞工法例的保障，可以享有如遣散費、長期服務金、有薪病假和有薪年假等勞工保障！<br />\n<br />\n4.18，有漏洞!<br />\n現時有不少老闆都會出盡辦法令工友不符合4.18的要求，例如安排工友頭3星期就不停做，但第４星期就分配少於18小時的工作，又或者斷斷續續在４星期間放假，大條道理唔俾福利，令好多兼職工友同散工都無法受勞工法例保障！<br />\n<br />\n雖然418存在咁多法律罅，但政府依然無意修改4.18法例，政府在05年以放寬4.18會提高老闆成本，令佢地請少D人為理由，拒絕放寬<br />\n4.18，而所謂的檢討亦由07年講到今年都未成事，究竟政府是幫工友，還是幫老闆?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://grassrootconcern.wordpress.com/2012/11/16/勞工法例知多d：418/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgrassrootconcern.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F11%2F16%2F%E5%8B%9E%E5%B7%A5%E6%B3%95%E4%BE%8B%E7%9F%A5%E5%A4%9Ad%EF%BC%9A418%2F&d=6mpiucgFL%2B7RJizNolVLEuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=bce9974f\" target=\"_blank\">https://grassrootconcern.wordpress.com/2012/11/16/勞工法例知多d：418/</a>"},{"pid":"a153e45c0aeea7accd57b4fc07954cba47e65f83","tid":533555,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8296f1a3794a42ad675f17de494389f51eec0a70","tid":533555,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:45:18.000Z","msg":"你仲想打政府工？<br />\n唔驚？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:47:44.000Z","msg":"唔驚"},{"pid":"0e9a61eb1591dd4851e2171160f94fb49ec3a1fb","tid":533555,"uid":6009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a153e45c0aeea7accd57b4fc07954cba47e65f83","tid":533555,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8296f1a3794a42ad675f17de494389f51eec0a70","tid":533555,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:45:18.000Z","msg":"你仲想打政府工？<br />\n唔驚？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:47:44.000Z","msg":"唔驚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:48:39.000Z","msg":"放心 呢份唔係政府工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8e1c9a2a0f57819799a7ed1f336d712e68e047","tid":533555,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T01:51:45.000Z","msg":"上個月先請完人，因乜解究咁快又請？"},{"pid":"36132a7fcea61e502f38102865371359eb2661c4","tid":533555,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-